<section class="py-20 bg-primary-600">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">RSS 订阅更新</h2>
      <p class="text-primary-100 mb-8">通过RSS获取最新文章和动态，第一时间掌握所有更新。</p>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input
          type="text"
          value="/rss.xml"
          readonly
          class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-transparent bg-white/10 text-white placeholder-primary-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20 transition-all duration-300"
        />
        <button
          onclick="window.location.href='/rss.xml';"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-primary-600 font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-50 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/20"
        >
          立即订阅
        </button>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-primary-100">
        订阅RSS，即可通过RSS阅读器接收最新更新。我们承诺保护您的隐私，绝不会向第三方泄露您的信息。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
